      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>REIMER-Lee. On May 4, 2000. Beloved husband of the late Sally; devoted father of Ilsa, Nina and Shelley (Craig Allen); adoring grandfather of Tyler, Justin and Jacob. Activist for justice, Yiddish raconteur and humorist, treasured for his kindness and generosity by all who knew him. Donations to the Southern Poverty Law Center. For information: 617-472-5888</p>
